Paper: hep-th/9205111

Date: 1992-05-29

Title: Extended form method of antifield-BRST formalism for BF theories

Authors: Hitoshi Ikemori

Comments: 8 pages, Shiga-92-1

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A7 (1992) 3397-3402

The Batalin-Vilkovisky antifield action for the BF theories is constructed bymeans of the extended form method. The BRST invariant BV antifield action isdirectly written down by making use of the extended forms that involve all therequired ghosts and antifields.